Put the two files (`sms-notifier.service` and `sms-notifier.timer`) into
`~/.config/systemd/user/` and run the following commands:

    $ systemctl --user enable --now sms-notifier.timer

You can manually trigger the notifier using

    $ systemctl --user start sms-notifier.service

To inspect the logs, use

    $ journalctl --user-unit sms-notifier.service
